casebody.data:
No. 35,

Orig.

United States v. Maine et al.

Report of the Special Master on the Massachusetts boundary is received and

ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Replies thereto, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days. [For earlier decision herein, see, e. g., 471 U. S. 375.]
